text: Olagbegi Atanneye I was a paramount ruler of Owo Kingdom, Ondo state, southwestern Nigeria who reigned between 1913 and 1938. He was the brother of Olowo Ajike Ogunoye and son of Olowo Olagbegi Atanneye II ==References== Category:Yoruba monarchs Category:Nigerian traditional rulers Category:People from Owo Category:Olagbegi family
title: Olagbegi Atanneye I
